    "title": "代币化激励经济学1：绩效支付简介[评论]",
    "slug": "economics-of-tokenized-incentives-1-intro-to-pay-for-performance",
    "authorName": "Crypto Clairity",
    "authorPicture": {
      "url": "https://www.datocms-assets.com/101962/1694589819-cryptoclaraty5.png"
    },
    "_publishedAt": "2023-10-05T09:15:12+01:00",
    "description": "深入探讨区块链平台中绩效支付激励的复杂性。了解成功的权衡和设计考量。",
    "thumbnail": {
      "url": "https://www.datocms-assets.com/101962/1690770568-cbc1-img1.png"
    },
    "contentBlock": [
      {
        "mainContent": {
          "value": {
            "schema": "dast",
            "document": {
